0118130225/http://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/2_Par/ch_18">18</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220118130225/http://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/2_Par/ch_19">19</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220118130225/http://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/2_Par/ch_20">20</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220118130225/http://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/2_Par/ch_21">21</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220118130225/http://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/2_Par/ch_22">22</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220118130225/http://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/2_Par/ch_23">23</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220118130225/http://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/2_Par/ch_24">24</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220118130225/http://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/2_Par/ch_25">25</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220118130225/http://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/2_Par/ch_26">26</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220118130225/http://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/2_Par/ch_27">27</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220118130225/http://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/2_Par/ch_28" class="active">28</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220118130225/http://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/2_Par/ch_29">29</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220118130225/http://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/2_Par/ch_30">30</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220118130225/http://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/2_Par/ch_31">31</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220118130225/http://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/2_Par/ch_32">32</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220118130225/http://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/2_Par/ch_33">33</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220118130225/http://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/2_Par/ch_34">34</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220118130225/ht